\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As we've seen, Dennett does not believe that there is such a thing as original
 or intrinsic intentionality.
 Akin to Searle not finding anything that could give his Chinese Room's
 homunculus any intrinsic intentionality that he could pass on to the system
 he is in, Dennett does not find any part of the human mind that could give
