\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
There are several theories that attempt to explain what we mean when we
 speak of knowledge.
 Considering it is always conscious minds that are interesting systems when
 we look at what knowledge is, and how nearly all epistemological research
 so far has been done from a human first-person perspective, we can quite
 safely say that epistemology
