\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Evolution might have worked a treat for life on earth and possibly elsewhere,
 but it certainly wasn't the best way to go about it.
 Minsky points out the following flaws of genetic, Darwinian evolution,
 saying that 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

it's so easy to improve evolution it's not funny
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Foot
status open

